<p>NOTES:</p>
<p>	 Both quarter periods for 1997 and 1996 include results</p>
<p>of NexStar Acquisition Inc which is being accounted for as</p>
<p>pooling of interests. The results of Technical Instruments</p>
<p>Co are included n consolidated results from August 8,</p>
<p>1996, the effective date of the acquisition, since it was</p>
<p>accounted for as a purchase.</p>
